{
  "stem": "15396.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was sorry because I'd liked him and I'd admired him so much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I admired his attitude, too, very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, you know, he was modest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think all of us, if we had been inclined to run around saying, oh, you know, I think we would have been hesitant because we knew Fry would not have done that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he died sort of-- and now, the newspapers are full of him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He'd been given the Legion d'Honneur from the French government, and Israel gave him the highest honor they can give.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I don't know, a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, he's been dead a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he wouldn't have done it for those things, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He didn't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he was-- he was pure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't have any-- inspiration, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And even if we-- I'm sure that a lot of things we did, we would have been ashamed not to have done them, and it was because of Fry as any other reason.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he really did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, at the Holocaust thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First time, yes, first time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have great admiration for Beamish, you know, [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hirschfeld, ?] Professor [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hirschfeld. ?] And also for [INAUDIBLE] and all these--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Mary Jane Gold, and Miriam Davenport [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very active.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mary Jane is doing a film on this subject.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the cassette that I gave, you know, about that-- that man who did that is going to do her story, and her story deals with this period, too.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she lives part of the time in the south of France, but most of the time in America.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
